      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">

        <p>
            I offer interactive workshops for universities, organisations, and teams on a range of topics such as <b>team dynamics, inclusivity, productivity, stress management, and change</b>.
        </p>
        <p>    
            The focus of workshops is usually on <b>psychoeducation combined with practical reflection and exercises</b>, so participants leave with new understanding, insights, and concrete next steps they can apply directly in their work, studies, or life.
            All workshops are <b>designed collaboratively</b> so they fully match your context, needs, and goals.
        </p>
        <p>
          I also welcome collaborations with small teams and early-stage organisations or co-founders, for example around communication, role clarity, and shared values.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
          <div>
            <h3 class="blueFont mt-0">Example Workshop Themes</h3>
            <p>
              <ul class="green-bullets space-y-1 [&>li]:my-0">
                <li>Career clarity sessions (e.g. Ikigai-based workshop)</li>
                <li>Team dynamics and communication</li>
                <li>Creating inclusive learning or working environments</li>
                <li>Overcoming procrastination</li>
                <li>Habit change and sustainable routines</li>
                <li>Managing stress and overwhelm</li>
              </ul>
            </p>
          </div>
        
          <div>
            <h3 class="blueFont mt-0">Format Types</h3>
            <p>
              Depending on your goals and context, workshops can range from highly interactive sessions with exercises and reflection,
              to more structured methodology-based formats or talks.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <h3 class="blueFont font-[Cambria]">How workshops are designed</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-lg prose-p:my-3">
      <ol class="list-decimal ml-6 space-y-4 green-numbers">
        <li>
          <strong>Initial Conversation</strong><br />
          After you reach out, we schedule a conversation to discuss your needs,
          ideas, and context, and see whether we are a good match.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Proposal and Price Estimate</strong><br />
          Based on our conversation, I prepare a price estimate and, if helpful,
          a first outline of the workshop or programme.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Alignment and Preparation</strong><br />
          Once we decide to work together, we align on goals and expectations and
          I further develop the workshop content. If useful, we can schedule an
          additional meeting to discuss specifics.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Workshop Delivery</strong><br />
          During the workshop, I create a safe and inclusive atmosphere and
          facilitate the session with structure while staying responsive to
          the group, allowing the programme to adapt slightly to emerging needs.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Reflection and Follow-up</strong><br />
            After the workshop, we reflect on how it went and what stood out.
            If useful, we discuss feedback, possible next steps, or follow-up
            sessions to support further learning or change.
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>



  

